listing_description:
Facing the beachfront in Dhoāpālong, Mermaid Beach Resort features a garden and a private beach area. Among the facilities at this property are room service and a 24-hour front desk, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The units come with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a fridge, a kettle, a shower, free toiletries and a wardrobe.
